{"tid":1614693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請不要對敵人仁慈","createTime":"2019-10-03T01:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T01:05:58.000Z","uid":173227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6db239d9071344fcbde8784f21f2463ca57a535d","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:02:07.000Z","msg":"2347 圖中藍絲路過大圍站表示會報警，有部分示威者表示想私了佢，其後被阻膠阻止，指：人地未出手就唔好喇。<br />\n<br />\n結果該藍絲真係報警，防暴立即到場。對峙一陣之後，防暴先推跌一名男子，再衝上前捉走一名男手足，又將另一名女途人壓响地。期間防暴公然非禮該女子，該女子大叫「救命呀！你做乜呀！非禮呀！」「我乜都冇做過！」。<br />\n<br />\n然後圍觀人士只係喝罵警察放人，然而該名女子最後冇被捕，但防暴帶走男手足。該名女子認識該名男手足，他被帶走期間女子不停衝入防暴防線大叫「救命呀！」，希望在埸人士救男手足，惟圍觀人士仍只係喝罵，冇嘗試救人。警方最後帶住男手足同增援會合，錯失救人時機。該名女子直至男手足上車前仍不停求救....<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，成個過程真係屌一聲，恭喜哂阻膠放過藍絲報警，同得個鬧字嘅人，多得呢班友，警方成功拉到男手足。女嘅拉個時已經非禮，如果不幸真係捉埋入警署今晚隨時俾黑警玩殘。大佬晚晚每次防暴人少突襲，捉完人每次都可以施施然冇穿冇爛咁帶住俘虜走到，真係覺得咁嘅結果OK？係盡咗力？<br />\n<br />\n#現場情況<br />\n#對敵人仁慈係對自己殘忍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/115172629861129/posts/130866261625099/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F115172629861129%2Fposts%2F130866261625099%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7IRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=f1e8253d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/115172629861129/posts/130866261625099/</a>"},{"pid":"d1b5dc18f1cf337708f7b098ef05f75507966bcb","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"8506e788ab12bbc46e96bf6ce2a7c63e7cdaecf1","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d4a348d3eaeefa840b61dde525cb3227881a7e","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:03:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258550eb329297565ee0263150efeafb8cde728e","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9b0ee4b0f7cd9809a5ee7457ee94b50a96fa7d","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aac8b71c85eb656e5c48f0a99fb4eb15dbc92c3","tid":1614693,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:04:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"583fb2b2a88bfccd76616de9fd603699e6ee3511","tid":1614693,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}